# OneWater Pakistan — Frontend Environment Variables
# All VITE_SUPABASE_* variables have been removed.
# The frontend now communicates exclusively through the Node.js/Express backend.

# In development: Vite proxy routes /api/* → http://localhost:5000 (see vite.config.ts)
# In production (Vercel): Set this to your Render backend URL
VITE_API_URL="http://localhost:5000"
